attributionInfo.agentName: Live in Luxury Real Estate Team

description: Exquisite waterfront 2 bed/2.5 bath condo at 50 Liberty, one of the Seaports most sought after luxury residences. Enjoy breathtaking views of Boston Harbor from your private balcony.  Elegant design and unparalleled amenities, this condominium offers a lifestyle of sophistication and comfort. This meticulously designed residence features top-of-the-line finishes complete with large breakfast bar, high-end white cabinetry, wine fridge, and appliances by Wolf, Sub Zero and Miele. Thoughtfully designed floor plan with 2 spacious bedrooms, each with its own custom walk in closet and en-suite bath.  Included with this home are 2 garage parking spaces and a storage unit.  Residents of 50 Liberty enjoy amenities such as 24/7 concierge, doorman, porter, fitness center, catering kitchen, and residence lounge with a terrace overlooking the harbor. Indulge in the vibrant lifestyle of the Seaport, surrounded by renowned dining, shopping, and entertainment options.
